metadata.name: The Path to Abstraction
metadata.description:
The shouting colors of her liberation as she finds the freedom to be herself.  
All her energies flowing from within her own true essence with no barriers or castration.  
She is a Free Woman.

Like the woman i represent, this artwork is also the birth of my artistic language.  
This was the Moment where i released myself from rules and dogmas to became a free thinking Artist able to create my own Art with my own specific artistic language.
